{"tid":2187102,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾鈺成：我不信香港死得 不少年輕人赴大灣區發展定居","createTime":"2020-09-03T12:02:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T13:31:24.000Z","uid":225130,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d67fe7c86ba57e6bcacc2f7a7b8cc6987fb77a7a","tid":2187102,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:02:23.000Z","msg":"曾鈺成：我不信香港死得 不少年輕人赴大灣區發展定居<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n曾鈺成今日下午接受劉慧卿訪問，直言不是全部香港年輕人均對香港前境感到暗淡，反而不少年輕人到了大灣區發展和定居，亦有大學生向他稱希望畢業後加入政府：「我就唔信香港會死得！」<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n劉慧卿問曾鈺成，若最終接受全民檢測的香港人不多，北京會否大鬧香港官員，曾鈺成反而認為京官應批評民主派，尤其是慫恿和嚇人不要參加檢測的人，因為在正常環境下，巿民應會接受檢測，問題是香港現時環境並不正常。劉慧卿指，若不是港府去年硬推送中條例，就不會令香港至今如此不正常。<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n他又指，美國總統特朗普不斷「唱衰」中國，說服全世界武漢肺炎起源於中國，意義不大。劉慧卿追問他是否相信武肺源自內地時，他拒作回應，只稱中國現時能控制疫情，反觀美國不能：「有啲人都話啦，你追究（中國）乜嘢吖？愛滋病係美國出嚟㗎！你追唔追究美國吖？」不過，翻查資料，較多說法指愛滋病乃是來自非洲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200903/OATGYDIEEZB7HFO2BKXTYTHQF4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3AGbSKeZyAO6ChIZSEcDTnWT1dRNFEdQwi1W_4LRcKAtBkFWPET0qzA8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200903%2FOATGYDIEEZB7HFO2BKXTYTHQF4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3AGbSKeZyAO6ChIZSEcDTnWT1dRNFEdQwi1W_4LRcKAtBkFWPET0qzA8E&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjRfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=23667de3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200903%2FOATGYDIEEZB7HFO2BKXTYTHQF4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3AGbSKeZyAO6ChIZSEcDTnWT1dRNFEdQwi1W_4LRcKAtBkFWPET0qzA8E&h=c0a417ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200903/OATGYDIEEZB7HFO2BKXTYTHQF4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_